 We live and breathe making the most of leisure moments and make it our mission to protect yours.<\/p>","text_size":"text-base"}}},"block_order":["heading_AMKaTR","text_tAgzaV"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.name","settings":{"color_scheme":"scheme-3","content_alignment":"center","padding_top":100,"padding_bottom":100,"show_section_divider":false,"divider_width":"fixed","custom_class":""}}},"order":["main","video_hero_riEjtc","image_with_text_p3XgXR","image_with_text_overlay_WV3dmM","rich_text_QYkRX4"]}
